==English==

===Noun===

# An [[actor]]/actress in [[movie]] that is generally known for starring in the [[genre]] of movies known as "[[action]]"
# An actor/actress portraying a [[character]] in a movie with action oriented scenes.
# The lead role of an "action" genre movie.
# An actor/actress in a movie in which contains [[special effects]], [[explosions]], [[choreographed]] fight scenes, etc.

===Usage Notes===
This is a Modern term - usually used as an adjective to describe people.